title: Suicides in Sweden in 2018 , by gender and age group
summary: You are viewing a chart of multi-line type with 2 lines denoting Men, and Women. The y axis indicates the Number of suicides in per 100 thousands and the x axis indicates Year.
Overall Men, and Women are gradually increasing,  throughout the Year
The lines ordered according to average values of Number of suicides in per 100 thousands in descending order is: 1. Men, and lastly, 2. Women.

Throughout the period, Men generally had the highest Number of suicides in per 100 thousands relative to others with an average of 177.8, and it reached its maximum at 15-44_years with a value of 361.0.
The botommost line, Women,  has a mean of 76.6, and peaked at 15-44_years.
